A van with 2,000 kilos of hashish passes the checkpoint in Alava
Five to ten in the morning.
The officers intimate the two occupants of a van who instead of stopping, flee.
Officers alerted the two occupants of a van who, instead of stopping, fled.
Their cargo, more than two tons of hashish, is a good reason not to stop.
