'Widening the boundaries of our last great northern frontier' is the long-term ambition of Jean Charest, presented yesterday in Levis, with tools with a strong visual impact, at the general council of the Liberal Party of Quebec.
Behind him, during his speech, the projection of a kind of "Mill with images".
